o.com/en/biografia-de-virginia-vallejo/ |title=Biography of the political asylee Virginia Vallejo |access-date=2018-04-30}}</ref> |- | 2011 | | [[Savva Terentyev]] | Estonia | Russian blogger and musician |<ref>[http://en.rian.ru/society/20110713/165176913.html Estonia grants political asylum to Russian blogger]</ref> |- | 2012 | [[File:Julian Assange full.jpg|75px]] | [[Julian Assange]] | Ecuador (embassy) | Australian editor, activist, publisher and journalist | Since 19 June 2012, he has been inside the [[Ecuadorian embassy in London]].<ref>[http://www.mmrree.gob.ec/2012/com042.asp Declaración del Gobierno de la República del Ecuador sobre la solicitud de asilo de Julian Assange] {{es icon}} ({{webarchive |url=https://www.webcitation.org/69xdGRSLN?url=http://www.mmrree.gob.ec/2012/com042.asp |date=16 August 2012 }})</ref> |- | 2012 | | [[Alexander Barankov]] | Ecuador | Belarusian former policeman or [[army captain]] |<ref name="belsat_29Jun2012_summary">{{cite web |last= |first= |authorlink= |title="Платформа" папрасіла Эквадор не выдаваць Баранкова |language=Belarusian |work= |publisher=[[Belsat TV]] |date=26 June 2012 |url=http://belsat.eu/be/wiadomosci/a,8916,platforma-paprasila-ekvador-nie-vydavats-barankova.html |doi= |accessdate=20 August 2012 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6A2rzSYBJ?url=http://belsat.eu/be/wiadomosci/a,8916,platforma-paprasila-ekvador-nie-vydavats-barankova.html |archivedate=19 August 2012 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref><ref name="expreso_15Aug2012">{{cite news |first= |last= |pages= |title=Corte analiza la extradición de bielorruso |date=15 August 2012 |publisher=[[List of newspapers in Ecuador|Expreso (Ecuador)]] |url=http://expreso.ec/expreso/plantillas/nota.aspx?idart=3597389&idcat=19408&tipo=2 |accessdate=20 August 2012 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6A2uXZjZ1?url=http://expreso.ec/expreso/plantillas/nota.aspx?idart=3597389&idcat=19408&tipo=2 |archivedate=20 August 2012 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref><ref name="TimeMag_16Aug20